Henry Houry https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Henry_Houry 0 Henry Houry (1874–1972) was a French stage actor. He also appeared in and directed films. He worked for a while in the United States during the silent era, directing the 1918 Corinne Griffith film Love Watches. Henry_Houry ( 1874 – 1972 ) was a_French_stage_actor .
